{"tid":1226943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真係夠了］究竟林鄭想死傷幾多人先收手？大家616一定要出黎","createTime":"2019-06-15T13:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:33:32.000Z","uid":70888,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3fffa8eaf9daa47d46fa050554d1ea1f741475","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"【引渡惡法】男子太古廣場掛橫額請願 消防拯救不果墮樓重創<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190615&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59719455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190615%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59719455&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=7651c437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190615%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59719455&h=76e62b73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190615&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59719455</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩知道依個新聞，真係好心酸，都係為左條仆街林鄭送中條例<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母林鄭，你想搞到幾多人死傷先安樂？？？<br />\n香港人唔該聽日616 一定要上街，一定要撤回送中，我地要幫依班義士拎返應有既交代同公義<br />\n林鄭我屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"c7de8e1f99068b1eac1c0e079cdeb2c4809ec166","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"f6ed42ea2ef528ba02d5623dd8a917e3d6e295d7","tid":1226943,"uid":36780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"忍不了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d283b061d7237cc2ea014e6394042463d8ef13cc","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"9c8ad024fd0658ea2220f2f2f51282f22d2cc3a7","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"c8d7e56b45a9bf9561651e7ba1767b1fbbbf658b","tid":1226943,"uid":123050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"490d5b2e40db743042ae04edfef7bdfd7277390e","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"8d7dac97ce728657d8b6aed8e23a44e5730c6df5","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"fbee41783fd353067523c9eafb17bf6a3a3b66d5","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"1f374b02d9eab4c276adfe0c16ec746876738019","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"f6d3e62ee5ac85cf3bbe03a5caadf512e833ebbd","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"75e52a835910e0f54d6d42464dd6ba015fc7078d","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"b6bf02f275fadc716edb3fdd613977cbe1907206","tid":1226943,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"唔撚出黎咪撚話香港人"},{"pid":"6920bfe6fc05be4ff32b56ec2e13a98ea8df6ae3","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"e362630f8712d168201dd584ed0338ed09f85302","tid":1226943,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:00:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭我屌你老母<br />\n聽日616一定要上街"},{"pid":"e8b42ab07f55cb2da7bed0b34e4b62db664dd0ae","tid":1226943,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6bf02f275fadc716edb3fdd613977cbe1907206","tid":1226943,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2